import React from "react";
import Sidebar from "../components/Sidebar";
import Topbar from "../components/Topbar";
import StatCard from "../components/StatCard";
import ActionCard from "../components/ActionCard";
import { Box, Grid, Typography } from "@mui/material";

export default function Dashboard({ mode, setMode }) {
  return (
    <Box sx={{ display: "flex" }}>
      <Sidebar />
      <Box sx={{ flex: 1 }}>
        <Topbar mode={mode} setMode={setMode} />
        <Box sx={{ p: 3 }}>
          <Typography variant="h4" fontWeight={700}>
            Dashboard Overview
          </Typography>
          <Typography variant="body1" mb={2} color="text.secondary">
            Railway operations management at a glance
          </Typography>
          {/* Stat Cards Grid */}
          <Grid container spacing={2}>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <StatCard label="Trains Ready" value="147" sublabel="180" icon="train" />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <StatCard label="Maintenance Alerts" value="8" sublabel="Active" icon="build" />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <StatCard label="Ad Deadlines" value="3" sublabel="This Week" icon="timer" />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <StatCard label="System Health" value="98.2%" sublabel="Uptime" icon="check_circle" />
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          {/* Quick Actions Section */}
          <Typography variant="h6" fontWeight={700} mt={4} mb={1}>
            Quick Actions
          </Typography>
          <Typography color="text.secondary" mb={2} variant="body2">
            Navigate to key operational areas
          </Typography>
          <Grid container spacing={2} mb={2}>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <ActionCard
                label="Data Prediction"
                description="View operational analytics"
                icon="chart"
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <ActionCard
                label="Maintenance Hub"
                description="Job cards and fitness tracking"
                icon="build"
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <ActionCard
                label="Train Audit"
                description="Detailed train profiles"
                icon="audit"
              />
            </Grid>
            <Grid item xs={12} sm={6} md={3}>
              <ActionCard
                label="Stabling Status"
                description="Bay allocation overview"
                icon="stabling"
              />
            </Grid>
          </Grid>
          
        </Box>
      </Box>
    </Box>
  );
}
